text: Georg Riedlsperger (born 6 May 1969) is an Austrian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Austria Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:People from St. Johann im Pongau District Category:Sportspeople from Salzburg (state)
